WHO   — The Wise Ones — the dreamwalkers and counselors of the Aiel
WHAT  — The women of wisdom, healing, and law among the Aiel — counselors whom even the fiercest clan chiefs heed.
WHERE — WOT · The Wheel of Time  Framework inputs: the Aiel  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — They are the true and quiet power of the Aiel, holding the people's law and memory through ji'e'toh.
HOW   — Many are dreamwalkers who enter and master Tel'aran'rhiod, the World of Dreams; some can channel, though they keep it hidden.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  The clan chiefs lead the spears; the Wise Ones decide where the spears will go.

